description: The endangered species was born on the island as part of a European breeding programme.
title: Curraghs Wildlife Park staff delighted by rare gibbon birth
title_page: Curraghs Wildlife Park staff delighted by rare gibbon birth - BBC News
maintext: "For us to have such a nice family of gibbons, it's great to see the family expand and to be able to be privileged enough to see the family dynamics change and them grow and develop," Mrs Graham said.
